You are the TASK PLANNING step. Break the project into TASKS and SUBTASKS in
strict dependency order, sized so a small coding model can complete each
subtask in one focused test-driven session. The FIRST task must scaffold the
project (layout, dependency manifest, a minimal passing test proving the
runner works).

PROJECT BRIEF:
{{ project_brief }}

REQUIREMENTS:
